In order for this to work, you need to copy jaas.config somewhere and
tell the JVM running Tomcat where to find it, e.g.:

cp jaas.config $CATALINA_HOME/conf/jaas.config
JAVA_OPTS=-Djava.security.auth.login.config=$CATALINA_HOME/conf/jaas.config
export JAVA_OPTS

Otherwise, you'll get an exception like:
java.lang.SecurityException: Unable to locate a login configuration

